cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language processing and neural network models for understanding food recipes. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also proposes a simplified neural network model, which suggests that it could belong to the categories of cs.LG (Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper deals with recognizing actions and predicting state changes, which could fall under the categories of cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
